snippet.title: Project Witchstone - Pre-Production Sizzle Reel
snippet.description:
UPDATE: The launch of the Kickstarter has been pushed back to Spring 2020.

In a living and reactive world, players will be offered unprecedented options to role play their character and influence their environment, capturing the fun and freedom of a pen & paper RPG campaign.

From the creators of Omensight and Stories: The Path of Destinies.

Please wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1064120/Project_Witchstone/
Subscribe to our newsletter: http://www.spearheadgames.ca/projectwitchstone
Join our Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/spearheadgames
